data.description: Welcome to the perfect haven! This stunning 5 bed, 3 bath home is the one you've been waiting for. Nestled in a serene friendly community, it offers everything you desire for comfortable living. Say goodbye to parking hassles with the spacious 3-car garage. The heart of the home, a chef's dream kitchen with sleek stainless steel appliances and a convenient walk-in pantry. A spacious backyard for endless  fun and entertaining, with a block wall offering privacy and security. Discover the lifestyle you've been dreaming of in this picture-perfect  retreat on a spacious corner lot . Don't miss this opportunity - come and explore your future home today!
